{"tid":1943700,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] MH-R モンハンライダーズ【14】 垃圾 Game 16 個鐘都冇人開新 Post","createTime":"2020-03-26T02:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T11:06:21.000Z","uid":113944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"203a91e3152b18b172ecfe0775a899176f1075ed","tid":1943700,"uid":113944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T02:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mobile.capcom.com/mh-r/assets/img/ud_200318/top.jpg?20200311042740\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.capcom.com%2Fmh-r%2Fassets%2Fimg%2Fud_200318%2Ftop.jpg%3F20200311042740&h=f0b69e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHomepage  <a href=\"https://mobile.capcom.com/mh-r/system.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.capcom.com%2Fmh-r%2Fsystem.html&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4W6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=ac02db0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.capcom.com/mh-r/system.html</a><br />\n公式Twitter  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MH_Riders\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMH_Riders&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4W6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=0fa93fc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MH_Riders</a><br />\n官方Wiki  <a href=\"https://kamigame.jp/mh-r/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkamigame.jp%2Fmh-r%2Findex.html&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4W6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=72069b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://kamigame.jp/mh-r/index.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/ad_img/1234690858743582721/53bsAOtl?format=png&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fad_img%2F1234690858743582721%2F53bsAOtl%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dsmall&h=7d54cbd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【首抽問題】</span></span></strong><br />\n【1】完成教學關卡及任抽的免費10連<br />\n（開局5星只建議以下2隻其中1隻,最多只會中1隻5星)<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/A79bgj7goI5y69eKAyy0p9aabBo9Mr3jbgJxZee6hYLt7iFy-5_NFI6pv8EhiAB4UlIMuFrG4a5mRjS8v4uEDoe8zjL5NHrMBhFa3GW79DhK=w120-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FA79bgj7goI5y69eKAyy0p9aabBo9Mr3jbgJxZee6hYLt7iFy-5_NFI6pv8EhiAB4UlIMuFrG4a5mRjS8v4uEDoe8zjL5NHrMBhFa3GW79DhK%3Dw120-rw&h=b8ae76cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LYm5TUPi4EWKpzIoMVQABUTElS0Y12Pm9YOnjXtbPcrSq0u-NoJ_KaZLj8RQdUT2K1q9ijGFs63RMM_rIGdB4YEja-6bL5I57iRzCaPDHqgOgg=w120-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FLYm5TUPi4EWKpzIoMVQABUTElS0Y12Pm9YOnjXtbPcrSq0u-NoJ_KaZLj8RQdUT2K1q9ijGFs63RMM_rIGdB4YEja-6bL5I57iRzCaPDHqgOgg%3Dw120-rw&h=d2c14bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2】開禮物箱,拎資源強化5星角色及3星雷狼龍過關用<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/fRQ6EFMOCNLam5ZvVgNzNF7IHRi-P7FIIB4DC-kUh1gJPRp-NtHKstSKQjJfnn8hlsUzw4x3SxwsM0zzkH4n7lGIAtBfM8bu=w120-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FfRQ6EFMOCNLam5ZvVgNzNF7IHRi-P7FIIB4DC-kUh1gJPRp-NtHKstSKQjJfnn8hlsUzw4x3SxwsM0zzkH4n7lGIAtBfM8bu%3Dw120-rw&h=69d42416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【3】盡快推主線完成Normal第2章，大概儲到2000石up<br />\n【4】之後只抽Step pool,搏以下是但一隻限定角<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(截3/11日 : 而家未有限定STEP POOL關係,建議留石) </span></strong><br />\n【5】滿意就一路清新手任務一邊拎報酬強化隊伍,繼續推主線完成Normal第4章<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/hxUewAR.jpg\" /><br />\n【6】然後開始刷每日素材本,限時活動及周末寶珠關卡<br />\n【7】逢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期五至日</span></strong>都會開週末寶珠關,新手建議先刷Rank上100UP加多D體,基本唔洗爆石無限升的<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">オトモン属性耐性表</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mhr/zokusei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmhr%2Fzokusei.jpg&h=3c1cd68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">育成必要寶玉/禮物數</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fr0eSD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffr0eSD4.jpg&h=1e798731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【常見問題】</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>◆護符有咩用,買左加護LV都唔升◆</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4nP8BF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4nP8BF.jpg&h=b952f4de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n各都市加護LV需要一定經驗值先會升,<br />\n而經驗值就係你BOX入面所有相對都市人既合計LV+合計護符數量,<br />\n人每升1LV=1EXP<br />\n護符1個=1EXP<br />\n所以護符買左就OK,咩都唔洗做 (數值上升フウガ最實用,加最多速)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>◆打邊關升RANK最好,升RANK有咩用◆</strong></span><br />\n①逢星期五-日開既寶玉關,如果你有以下隻5星奇猿仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mhr/uploads/2020/02/2020y02m20d_2023592887.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmhr%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F2020y02m20d_2023592887.jpg&h=8f0d02c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就刷寶玉第3關 = 得佢招水技可一下秒黑狼 (8體160EXP)<br />\n無既話刷第2關 = 是但搵隻最大力既都秒到 (7體140EXP)<br />\n<br />\n②活動半體既時間建議刷主線maniac1-3,可順便打埋素材<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0US6bPi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0US6bPi.jpg&h=09135306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>◆龍可唔可以換比其他人◆</strong></span><br />\n去強化&rarr;オトモン譲渡<br />\n每換一次要用一張譲渡卷,但d卷可任刷/活動換得又有,唔洗刻意慳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>◆換唔換迅龍好,換1隻定2隻好◆</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/D8pJPpJgLdzjuYd2dHi79ivQri-RqkTGHEkhTpyP1IDdzAJWDOqTWUoHQ0kwe_uTK-Ow0rPeXDSlVIO30mnR6nIkiivfR_o=rw\" /><br />\n★稀少價值高 : 5星龍基本能力值比起3,4星高好多<br />\n★較容易育成 : 5星專用玉交換所可用50 NEKO PT換到,易升60LV<br />\n★無屬性攻擊 : 對全屬敵人等倍傷害唔會半減,汎用性高<br />\n★高會心機率 : 技「テイルドロップ」「テイルブレード」易發動會心1.5倍傷害+特性HP50%以下會心傷害增加,逆境自強<br />\n★主水屬耐性 : 自帶50%水屬耐性,對轟龍有傷害半減優勢<br />\n★自帶減防技 : 25SP發動回轉率高,唔會同人技重疊<br />\n<br />\n結論 : 建議換1隻"},{"pid":"11480fc03c6ef737769aca0c38b46d830da59278","tid"